window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>War is here…but so is Jerry!</p> <p>Jerry and his friends sail for the Wild Continent, where another Prism hides. But so do strange tribes, traitors, and old gods....</p> <p>Meanwhile, Jericho hunts necromancers, the Death Primordial reigns, and the Order is rapidly dominating the world. As all forces converge at the Sea of Sands, can Jerry and his friends make it in time?</p> <p>The only way to defeat a God…might well be shoes!</p> <p>Book three of this laugh-fueled new slice-of-death Progression Fantasy by Valerios, best-selling author of <i>Road to Mastery</i>. Follow Jerry down his path of necromancy as he grows in power, proving his unorthodox methods may hold a lot more merit than it seems.</p>"; 
